Nate Ledbetter <ltdomer98@...> wrote:

--- Rod Pavez <grfkboyz@...> wrote:

> Hey there everybody:
> Quick question about musuems in Japan. I don't know
> if this question 
> qualifies but I was wondering if there are any
> museums in Japan that 
> specialize in western culture dealing with art and
> so forth.
> I looked through the internet but came up dry. Just
> wondering if 
> anybody knew.
> Thanks

Quite a few, actually. Plenty of modern art museums,
etc. Hakone has an open air sculpture museum, with
sections of Picasso. Yokohama has several, Tokyo also.
